The paper discusses the use of IaaS clouds for computational workloads, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The focus on service-oriented environments suggests a connection to Computer Engineering (cs.CE) and Networked Systems (cs.NI). The use of software to manage the cloud cluster suggests a connection to Software Engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper's focus on distributed systems and cloud computing suggests a connection to Distributed Systems (cs.Distributed Systems).
